en_187483_0	Former DIG Vass Gunawardena and 5 others who are accused of having in possession firearms illegally, were released on bail today (Apr. 02).
en_187483_1	The case relating to this was taken up at the Colombo High Court.
en_187483_2	They were granted bail on a cash bail of Rs.
en_187483_3	10,000 and 2 personal bails of Rs.
en_187483_4	200,000 each.
en_187483_5	Earlier, they had submitted a revised bail application.
en_187483_6	DIG Vass Gunawardena was earlier found guilty of murdering businessman Mohammed Shyam.
